OL,3,CMother appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurdering six-year-old boy
OL,6,FA mother has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering her son and attempting
OL,8,Fto murder her father.
OL,10,FKarolina Zurawska, 41, from Gendros,
OL,11,FSwansea, appeared before the city's
OL,12,Fcrown court on Friday morning.
OL,14,FShe is charged with murdering
OL,15,FAlexander Zurawski, six, who was found
OL,16,Fdead at a property in Gendros on
OL,17,FAugust 29.
