OL,3,CMother appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurdering six-year-old boy
OL,6,FThe defendant is also accused of
OL,7,Fattempting to murder her father,
OL,8,FKrzysztof Siwi, 67, earlier the same
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,FZurawska appeared via video link from
OL,12,Fcustody for the short administrative
OL,13,Fhearing before Judge Paul Thomas.
OL,15,FShe was not asked to enter pleas to
OL,16,Fthe two charges against her.
OL,18,FThe judge vacated the trial date of
OL,19,FFebruary 17 to allow for further
OL,20,Freports to take place.
