OL,6,FA mention hearing for the case will
OL,7,Ftake place instead on February 17 at
OL,8,FSwansea Crown Court.
OL,10,FJudge Thomas told the court: "I hope
OL,11,Fon that date there will be progress in
OL,12,Fone way or another, if only in terms
OL,13,Fof fixing a new trial date."
OL,15,FMike Jones KC appeared for the
OL,16,Fprosecution during the hearing, while
OL,17,FJohn Hipkin KC represented Zurawska.
