OL,6,FIn a statement issued by South Wales
OL,7,FPolice following his death,
OL,8,FAlexander's family described him as a
OL,9,F"very kind child".
OL,11,F"Alexander was always well-behaved and
OL,12,Fnever naughty," they said.
OL,14,F"He was very clever and very mature
OL,15,Ffor his age. He had great
OL,16,Funderstanding of facts.
OL,18,F"Alexander was always helpful, always
OL,19,Feager to assist with cooking and
OL,20,Fcleaning.
